      "rationale": "At MRL 3 for a Class II device, SQA requires documented version control and regression testing. The FE solver (Abaqus 2023) is FDA-cleared for structural analysis; internal SQA records confirm ISO 9001:2015-compliant version control, automated regression test suite covering 47 contact mechanics benchmarks, and documented change management. Achieved level 3 reflects additional traceability of analysis scripts under configuration management.",
