      "rationale": "All material properties sourced from peer-reviewed literature and manufacturer data sheets with documented traceability. UHMWPE Ogden parameters calibrated from uniaxial tensile tests on three specimens from the same material lot (GUR 1050, 50 kGy). Uncertainty distributions assigned to all eight sensitivity-identified inputs based on literature variability data or experimental characterization. Monte Carlo propagation (n=1000) performed to quantify input uncertainty contribution to QoI uncertainty. Achieved level 3 reflects formal uncertainty characterization and propagation for all primary inputs.",
